description: Expository Bible teaching from Denton Bible Church. Solid truth from God's Word that is timeless and boundless. This podcast features the weekly Sunday sermons from Denton Bible Church featuring pastor and author Tommy Nelson. For more information or to purchase a copy of what you hear on audio cd or DVD video follow the link below or call us toll free 1-866-322-8273. We are a donation based ministry so we welcome your donations should you feel lead to give. Denton Bible Church is committed to the worldwide equipping of the saints for the work of the ministry to the glory of God!
